<item>
            <title>[HBASE-4240] Allow Loadbalancer to be pluggable.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4240</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Everyone seems to want something different from a load balancer.  People want low latency, simplicity, and total control.  It seems like at some point the load balancer can&apos;t be all things to all people.  Something akin to what hadoop JT&apos;s pluggable scheduler seems like it will enable all solutions without making the code much more complex. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
